'''Write a program to calculate the total cost
of a meal, including tax and tip, based on user input for the meal cost
and percentage rates for tax and tip.'''

tc=int(input("Enter the cost of meal : "))
tax=int(input("Enter the tax to be paid(%) : "))
tip=int(input("Enter the tip amnt : "))
fc=tc+(tax/100)*tc+tip
print("Total cost of the meal is : ",fc)
